{"tid":1119252,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"簡單好食嘅齋菜","createTime":"2019-04-21T19:30:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T15:57:52.000Z","uid":111088,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"eff2f5474e48a2c5cc75a62c1c6eedfa7bf446b1","tid":1119252,"uid":111088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T19:30:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AupBfqs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAupBfqs.jpg&h=9d4379c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nsor for垃圾攝影技術<br />\n呢個係喺齋鋪食嘅<br />\n佢係一個完整木瓜批左個頂刮曬啲籽然後擺一堆青瓜沙律入個窿度(就真係青瓜+沙律醬咁簡單)，然後擺少少素肉鬆同紫菜喺上面<br />\n可能因為木瓜當造，陣甜味同青瓜嗰個清新好夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係食齋嘅大家可以試吓鋪蟹子<br />\n應該會再好味啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"173679adc962e7cf7f3e5842d822d95ddfd74de7","tid":1119252,"uid":111088,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T19:35:36.000Z","msg":"真心好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a4cb39c9d5da1e5a1e70a0e450699ed5af220a9","tid":1119252,"uid":80173,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T04:08:13.000Z","msg":"邊間"},{"pid":"3d860a8805d43b2a8eddc468eaae8e7058d7d7e9","tid":1119252,"uid":111088,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8a4cb39c9d5da1e5a1e70a0e450699ed5af220a9","tid":1119252,"uid":80173,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T04:08:13.000Z","msg":"邊間"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T04:36:38.000Z","msg":"大自然"},{"pid":"cb8f2782c3e0d7098f314b87968df87163cc3c52","tid":1119252,"uid":111088,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8a4cb39c9d5da1e5a1e70a0e450699ed5af220a9","tid":1119252,"uid":80173,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T04:08:13.000Z","msg":"邊間"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T04:52:56.000Z","msg":"不過其實自己都做到"}